high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the freezer into three pieces.
Look down to face the bottom of the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Look up to face the freezer.
Pick up an apple piece in the freezer.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the cabinet above the sink.
Place the piece of apple in a bowl in the cabinet above the sink.
Pick up the bowl with the apple piece in it from the cabinet above the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn left to face the fridge.
Place the bowl with a piece of apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put an apple in a bowl and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the white table directly in front of you.
Pick up the knife that has the blade facing you off of the table.
Turn to the right and move to the fridge on the left.
Open the freezer and close it after slicing the apple.
Face the fridge.
Place the knife into the fridge.
Face the freezer.
Open the freezer and take out a slice of the apple.
Turn around and move to the cupboard above the sink on the right.
Place the apple in the bowl in the cupboard.
Take out the bowl with the apple inside from the cupboard.
Turn around and move to the fridge on the left.
Place the bowl with the apple inside into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple slice into a bowl and place it inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the end of the table and hang a right, go to the white table across the room.
Pick up the rightmost yellow handled knife from the table.
Hang a right and head to the fridge.
Cut the apple inside the freezer into pieces.
Back up from the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Move forward to the freezer.
Take a piece of the apple out of the freezer.
Turn around, go to the stove, hang a right and head to the sink.
Put the apple inside the bowl that is in the right hand cupboard above the sink.
Take the bowl containing the apple out of the cupboard.
Turn around, go to the wall, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the bowl inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl containing a piece of apple in the fridge.
